    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) optimized for performance. The heart of this machine is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a Double VANOS system that has been recently serviced for optimal cam timing. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To address common platform weaknesses, this chassis has been professionally fitted with rear subframe reinforcement plates. The suspension geometry is enhanced by adjustable coilovers, providing superior damping and reduced body roll during high-G cornering. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a 'good' condition driver, the powertrain and drivetrain remain tight, offering the high-revving, visceral experience this M-car is known for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
